<HEADLINE> Bush Fire Rage on Mount Kilimanjaro </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, October 4 (Xinhua) -- The U.N. warned on Friday that
bush fires raging on Mount Kilimanjaro had now devastated about
