<HEADLINE> Urgent: Nepali Government Collapses </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, October 4 (Xinhua) -- The seven-month-old coalition
government of Nepal led by Lokendra Bahadur Chand collapsed
Saturday afternoon after the Lower House passed by 107-94 a
no-confidence motion against the government tabled by the main
opposition Nepali Congress.  
</P>
