<HEADLINE> Bangladesh's Parties to Clash Over Road Plan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, October 4 (Xinhua) -- The ruling Awami League (AL) is
set to be in conflict with its arch rival Bangladesh Nationalist
Party (BNP) over a countrywide railroad barricade plan, to be
enforced by the latter on October 5.
</P>
