environmental surveillance, said the Brazilian Space Agency (AEB).
</P>
<P>
After the successful launching of the SCD-1, its first
satellite in orbit, Brazil concentrates now on the launching at
the end of October of the second SCD2a Series satellite by the
Brazilian rocket VLS, said the AEB.
</P>
<P>
