<HEADLINE> Jamaica, United States Draw in World Cup Qualifier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 3 (Xinhua) -- Jamaica forced the United
States to a 1-1 draw in a World Cup qualifier on Friday.
</P>
