The details for withdrawing 1,100 French troops from the country's
capital Bangui was still being worked out.
</P>
<P>
France has two military bases in the Central Africa Republic.
The bases were set up in accordance with the defense agreement
signed in 1960s between the two countries. (Cameroun-Troop
Withdrawal)
